title: Loving Lover Was Burning Red (xoxo Lover)
description:
We can't believe we are here already! Let's send the Lover era off in a good way! Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey rank their top 5 songs from Lover.
How does your list compare? And how excited is everyone for Red? We absolutely CANNOT wait to deep dive into that album!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to contact us!
